---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="未找到" description="页面不存在">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">你走到了空白页</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">这个角落还没有内容，先回主页慢慢探索。</p>
    <a class="button-pop mt-6 inline-flex rounded-full border border-black/10 px-5 py-2 text-sm text-slate-600" href="/">
      返回首页
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
